<item>
            <title>[HIVE-10564] webhcat should use webhcat-site.xml properties for controller job submission</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-10564</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;webhcat should use webhcat-site.xml in configuration for the TempletonController map-only job that it launches. This will allow users to set any MR/hdfs properties that want to see used for the controller job.&lt;br/&gt;
NO PRECOMMIT TESTS&lt;/p&gt;</description>
